# Podman

> Podman is a plug'n'play docker replacement

- Sets the default machine podman will use (kinda)
`podman system connection default <machine-name>`

- Clones a docker image
`podman pull <image>`

- Attach interactively to a running container
`podman start -ia <container-name>`

- Publish port
`podman run -p [hostport]:[containerport]`
